Download GROSS FIXED CAPITAL FORMATION BY SECTOR AND TYPE OF GOOD

get_fbkf.Rd

Get the series of the gross fixed capital formation by sector and type of good of the Dominican Republic.

Usage

get_fbkf()

Value

a data frame with monthly series

Examples

get_fbkf()
